üöÄ Quick Start Example
bash
Copy
Edit
# 1. Install Ollama
brew install ollama     # macOS
# or on Linux:
curl https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh

# 2. Pull a model
ollama pull llama2

# 3. Run it
ollama run llama2

# 4. Or run a server
ollama serve
# then interact via REST or Python
This gives you full conversational capability on your local machine 
